 4px;\">15</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":15,\"repo\":\"sheadawson/silverstripe-userswitcher\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Adds a small form both in the frontend and backend to quickly login as any user.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-08T10:22:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Very Useful Modules</h2><h3>Development Helpers</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/dhensby/silverstripe-masquerade\">Masquerade</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/dhensby/silverstripe-masquerade\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">14</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":14,\"repo\":\"dhensby/silverstripe-masquerade\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> -  Allows an Administrator to \"login\" as another \"Member\". This can be useful for debugging and remote support.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-08T10:22:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Very Useful Modules</h2><h3>Fancy Form Fields</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Silverstripers/markdownfield\">Markdown Field</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Silverstripers/markdownfield\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">10</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":10,\"repo\":\"Silverstripers/markdownfield\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> -  Can replace your HTMLEditorFields (using TinyMCE) so you can utilise Markdown syntax.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-08T10:22:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Very Useful Modules</h2><h3>Fancy Form Fields</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/nathancox/silverstripe-codeeditorfield\">Code Editor Field</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/nathancox/silverstripe-codeeditorfield\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">25</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":25,\"repo\":\"nathancox/silverstripe-codeeditorfield\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> -  Gives you a syntax-highlighted text area field - great for CMS-based YAML or HTML.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-08T10:22:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2><h4>Vagrant</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Zauberfisch/vagrant-boxes\">Zauberfisch Vagrant Boxes</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Zauberfisch/vagrant-boxes\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">6</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":6,\"repo\":\"Zauberfisch/vagrant-boxes\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> -  Preconfigured Vagrant boxes for SS3 and SS4.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-08T10:22:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2><h4>Docker</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://hub.docker.com/r/brettt89/silverstripe-web\">brettt89/silverstripe-web</a> -  Apache + PHP Docker image with pre-installed PHP modules for SilverStripe support.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-08T10:22:32.000Z"},{"categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2><h4>Docker</h4>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://hub.docker.com/r/brettt89/silverstripe-solr-cwp\">brettt89/silverstripe-solr-cwp</a> -  CWP Solr Docker image.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-10-08T10:22:32.000Z"}]},"previous":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/MartinMiles/awesome-sitecore","repo":"MartinMiles/awesome-sitecore"},"next":{"id":"awesomes/github.com/directus-community/awesome-directus","repo":"directus-community/awesome-directus"}},"pageContext":{"repo":"wernerkrauss/awesome-silverstripe-cms","id":"awesomes/github.com/wernerkrauss/awesome-silverstripe-cms","previousId":"awesomes/github.com/MartinMiles/awesome-sitecore","nextId":"awesomes/github.com/directus-community/awesome-directus"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","2828988102"]}